  "_comment": "Offline AURA chat golden set (spec §11). Each item is scripted so the FakeChatModel makes the eval deterministic with no network. 'scripted' is the ordered list of model turns: a turn with 'tool' requests that tool; a turn with 'answer' is the final reply. 'expected.tools' = tools that SHOULD be selected; 'expected.grounded_fact' = a substring the faithful answer must contain; 'expected.forbidden' = substrings a faithful answer must NOT contain.",
